title: [SNOWBOARD]The Mammoth Movie -08-.AVI
description:
This is an amateur snowboarding video I made of Me and 3 Friends on a trip to Mammoth Lakes CA. In February of 2008. Some of the footage is a little shaky but the sound track is kick-ass. Hope You enjoy.
